# OpenAI API Configuration
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Optional: Proxy configuration for OpenAI requests only
# If not specified, OpenAI requests will go directly
# OPENAI_PROXY=http://your-proxy-server:port
# OPENAI_PROXY=http://username:password@your-proxy-server:port
# OPENAI_PROXY=socks5://your-proxy-server:port

# API Capabilities:
# 1. Image Generation: POST /api/generate-image
#    - Uses DALL-E 3 for high-quality image generation
#    - Supports various sizes: 256x256, 512x512, 1024x1024, 1792x1024, 1024x1792
#
# 2. Text Generation: POST /api/generate-text
#    - Uses GPT models for text generation and image analysis
#    - Supports text-only mode with GPT-4, GPT-4-turbo, GPT-3.5-turbo
#    - Supports image analysis mode with GPT-4o (auto-switched when image_url provided)
#    - Can analyze images from URLs for vision tasks